{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c35fc7c8d4","title":"迟群传达的江青的电话指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"548f9f5f6a","index":0,"year":1975,"month":4,"day":4,"articleId":"c35fc7c8d4"}],"tags":[{"id":"1020d14f10","name":"迟群","type":"人物"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"jqjianghua","name":"江青十年讲话汇编","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"江青，本世纪初国内老左编","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/jqjianghua.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"},{"id":"45fc78cde4","name":"迟群"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9cd1649cc9","type":"title","text":"迟群传达的江青的电话指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c35fc7c8d4"},{"id":"5528dd58f8","type":"authors","text":"江青迟群","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c35fc7c8d4"},{"id":"c8cbe94a15","type":"paragraph","text":"我昨天接见工人同志们的讲话中，可能有不全面，不适合的地方，请同志们充分地讨论提出意见。因为完全没有睡好觉。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c35fc7c8d4"},{"id":"8ce407b952","type":"paragraph","text":"另外，我讲了春桥同志关于对资产阶级全面专政文章的重点。我还要补充另一个重点，就是现在我们的主要危险不是教条主义，而是经验主义，这个问题进城以后就屡次提出过，在全党没有提起应有的警惕。现在我们应该按照毛主席的教导，对经验主义的危险性，擦亮眼睛，要认识清楚，保持高度警惕。经验主义是修正主义的帮凶，是当前的大敌。共产党员、共青团员如不很好地学习马列主义、毛泽东思想，提高识别经验主义的鉴别力，否则就会变修。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c35fc7c8d4"}],"page":{"id":"3499e10a8c","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"c35fc7c8d4","start":0,"end":0}},"jqjianghua":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"362a812dff","type":"title","text":"迟群传达的江青的电话指示","index":0,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c35fc7c8d4"},{"id":"74686f9f43","type":"paragraph","text":"我昨天接见工人同志们的讲话中，可能有不全面，不适合的地方，请同志们充分地讨论提出意见。因为完全没有睡好觉。","index":1,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"c35fc7c8d4"},{"id":"a39ae81808","type":"